### Dotfiles Intstallation:

  **Step 1:** `cd ~`
  **Step 2:** `git clone git://github.com/jdpagley/dotfiles`

### Create symlinks

  `ln -s ~/dotfiles/.vimrc ~/.vimrc`
  `ln -s ~/dotfiles/.vim ~/.vim`
  `ln -s ~/dotfiles/.gitconfig ~/.gitconfig`
  `ln -s ~/dotfiles/.gitignore ~/.gitignore`
  `ln -s ~/dotfiles/.bash_profile ~/.bash_profile`

### Installing Plugins

  **Step 1:** Make sure you're in the root of the dotfiles directory.
  **Step 2:** Type `git submodule init`. This registers the submodules.
  **Step 3:** Type `git submodule update`. This checks out the version of the plugins that you have committed to the dotfiles.

  Detailed Resource: http://vimcasts.org/episodes/synchronizing-plugins-with-git-submodules-and-pathogen/


